{"article_id":"y3D4fkW8WMb4y6Bf","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"By bulldozing into Roger Stone 's sentencing ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"Donald Trump sparked a mutiny by four career prosecutors ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"raised fears about the impartial administration of justice","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"and showed how his impeachment acquittal unchained an already rampant presidency .","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"The Justice Department 's decision","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"to water down a recommendation by its own prosecutors","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"for Stone to serve up to nine years in prison","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"that outraged the President","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"sent shockwaves through Washington .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"It also appears to reflect Trump 's redoubled determination","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"to escalate pressure on core institutions of the US government","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to pursue his personal and political priorities .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Wednesday morning , he brazenly offered congratulations to Attorney General Bill Barr","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"for `` taking charge of a case","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that was totally out of control","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"and perhaps should not have even been brought , ''","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"even though multiple courts have upheld former special counsel Robert Mueller 's appointment , his authority , and the decisions","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"he made .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"The sudden storm over Stone ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"triggered by an early-hours tweet by the President ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"is part of an accelerating pattern of unmoderated behavior","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"since Trump was found not guilty of impeachable offenses a week ago by Republican senators","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"-- some of whom expressed the hope","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"that the scar of impeachment would temper his wildest impulses .","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"Instead , the President appears to have drawn a lesson about impunity from his experience","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"and seems committed to accelerating his bid","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"to subvert constitutional and political norms .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"This may augur a period of expansive power plays by the President","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"-- as he runs for reelection","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"and that could become even more intense","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"if he wins a second term .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"In another sign of his defiance , Trump last week fired officials ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"including White House Ukraine specialist Lt. Col Alexander Vindman ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"who were subpoenaed to testify in the impeachment inquiry in a manner","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"that might have been interpreted as witness intimidation in a regular context","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"and is likely to chill future accountability .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"On Tuesday , he said","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that he would `` certainly '' expect the military to look at disciplining Vindman ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"who testified","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"that he was troubled by the President 's call with Ukraine 's President in July .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Trump has also launched searing personal attacks on senators","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"who voted to convict him ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"and questioned the faith of House Speaker Nancy Pelosi ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"who led the impeachment process there .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Stone was convicted by a jury of lying to Congress and witness tampering .","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"The Justice Department reversal","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"that triggered the remarkable resignations of four top prosecutors in the case","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"could fuel an impression","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"that cronies of the President can commit crimes","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"and get special treatment .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"It also poses the question","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"of whether political appointees are undercutting the work of career prosecutors in a way","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"that could prejudice the rule of law .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"`` This is completely stunning .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"I have seen thousands of cases in my career as a federal and state prosecutor .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"I have never seen anything like this , ''","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"CNN legal analyst Elie Honig told Jake Tapper .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"`` It stinks to high hell .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"There are all sorts of problems here .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"This is not normal . ''","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Trump denied","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"he had asked the Justice Department to lower the sentencing recommendations","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"concerning Stone","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"but he said","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"that the idea","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"that his longtime friend and fixer should spend up to nine years in prison","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"was ridiculous","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"and attacked the federal prosecutors","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"who conducted the case .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"`` I thought","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"the whole prosecution was ridiculous","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"and I look at others","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"who have n't been prosecuted .","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"That was a horrible aberration ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"these ,","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"I guess","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"the same Mueller people","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"who put everybody through hell , ''","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"the President said .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Trump also risked exacerbating the controversy","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"by insisting","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"although he had n't barged into the Stone case","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"`` I 'd be able to do it","depth":16},{"id":85,"text":"if I wanted . ''","depth":16},{"id":86,"text":"`` I have the absolute right","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"to do it , ''","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"Trump said in a previously unscheduled appearance before reporters .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Trump 's comment ignored the fact","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"as he often has in other contexts ,","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"he made his move on Stone in plain sight","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"-- in a tweet --","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"rather than in some suspicious behind-the-scenes intervention .","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"Even if the Justice Department was not reacting directly to the President 's desires ,","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"the impression","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"that it was","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"is just as damaging .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"The impartial administration of justice does not just require actual separation between politics and the law .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"The Justice Department 's reputation and the credibility of the rule of law rests on the impression","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"that such a situation prevails .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"The President 's move crystallized the argument of Democrats","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"competing in Tuesday 's New Hampshire primary","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"that Trump","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"-- through such actions","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"as firing former FBI chief James Comey over the Russia probe --","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"constantly abuses his power .","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"`` It is outrageous that DOJ has deeply damaged the rule of law","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"by withdrawing its recommendation .","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"Stepping down of prosecutors should be commended","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"& actions of DOJ should be investigated , ''","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"Pelosi wrote .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"But such criticism is unlikely to harm Trump among his most committed supporters ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"who have bought into his claims of `` dirty cops '' and `` scum ''","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"operating in a `` Deep State '' at the Justice Department .","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"Reporter to Trump :","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"Did you ask DOJ about Roger Stone ?","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"Reporter to Trump :","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"Did you ask DOJ about Roger Stone ?","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"01:08","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"The highly unusual episode over Stone will also fuel concerns among legal experts","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"that Barr is functioning increasingly as a political functionary for Trump .","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"The department said","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"there was no coordination with the White House on Stone 's sentence .","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"Yet the President 's public tweet leaves the clear impression","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"that he is meddling in the case .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"Trump has made no secret of his view","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"that the Justice Department should pursue his political enemies and protect him .","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"Multiple recent actions by Barr have appeared to favor the President","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"and tarnished the department 's reputation for the impartial administration of justice","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"-- a pillar of the political system .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"In recent days , Barr has said","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"his department is looking at information","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"provided by Trump 's personal lawyer Rudy Giuliani","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"alleging misconduct by Joe Biden and his son in Ukraine .","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"Trump and his allies have repeatedly made unfounded and false claims","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"to allege","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"that the Bidens acted corruptly in Ukraine .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"Barr has also warned","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"that federal investigations into political campaigns must be vetted by the senior political leadership at Justice .","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"Barr named US Attorney John Durham","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"to investigate the origin of the FBI 's investigation into links between the Trump campaign and Russia , after calls for such a probe by the President .","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"In his most controversial intervention , Barr wrote to Congress last year about the conclusions of Mueller 's report","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"before it was released ,","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"prompting the special counsel to complain","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"that the Attorney General did not capture the character of his findings .","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"Career prosecutors","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"handling the Stone case","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"made an aggressive sentencing recommendation of seven to nine years in prison over a conviction","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"based on seven charges .","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"But a senior Justice Department official told CNN","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"the finding was `` extreme and excessive '' and disproportionate to Stone 's offenses","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"and was not communicated to department leaders .","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"The backtrack came","depth":7},{"id":158,"text":"after Trump sent out a tweet","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"complaining about the recommendation in the middle of the night .","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"`` This is a horrible and very unfair situation .","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"The real crimes were on the other side ,","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"as nothing happens to them .","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"Can not allow this miscarriage of justice ! ''","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"Trump wrote .","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"The tweet immediately sparked fresh speculation","depth":6},{"id":166,"text":"that the President would use his executive powers","depth":7},{"id":167,"text":"to pardon Stone","depth":8},{"id":168,"text":"-- whose attorneys had argued for a maximum sentence of 15 to 21 months .","depth":8},{"id":169,"text":"The final decision on sentencing will be left to the judge in the case Amy Berman Jackson .","depth":5},{"id":170,"text":"Some legal experts have said","depth":7},{"id":171,"text":"that the seven to nine years recommendation was harsh ,","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"though it was the product of a table of sentencing guidelines .","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"In an updated filing to the court late Tuesday afternoon , the department did not specify","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"how much jail time it wanted to receive","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"but called for a sentence for `` far less ''","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"than it had originally requested .","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":4},{"id":178,"text":"Ex-prosecutor on Roger Stone :","depth":5},{"id":179,"text":"This stinks to high hell","depth":5},{"id":180,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":4},{"id":181,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":5},{"id":182,"text":"Ex-prosecutor on Roger Stone :","depth":7},{"id":183,"text":"This stinks to high hell","depth":7},{"id":184,"text":"01:10","depth":6},{"id":185,"text":"The swift reaction to the Stone controversy from top Democrats signaled","depth":5},{"id":186,"text":"the House still intends to wield its checks and balances powers","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"to seek to constrain Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":188,"text":"even given the failure of the impeachment effort","depth":7},{"id":189,"text":"to oust him from office .","depth":7},{"id":190,"text":"Senate Democratic minority leader Chuck Schumer called on the Justice Department 's inspector general to launch an investigation .","depth":6},{"id":191,"text":"House Judiciary Chairman Jerry Nadler , a New York Democrat , said","depth":8},{"id":192,"text":"that his panel would investigate the Stone sentencing matter .","depth":8},{"id":193,"text":"`` A President","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"who intervenes in the criminal justice system","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"to help his allies ,","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"while punishing people like Lt. Col. Vindman","depth":11},{"id":197,"text":"for telling the truth ,","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"represents a real danger","depth":9},{"id":199,"text":"and the Committee will get to the bottom of this , '' Nadler tweeted .","depth":8},{"id":200,"text":"The lead House impeachment manager , California Democratic Rep. Adam Schiff ,","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"who warned senators during the trial","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"that Trump 's acquittal would prompt the President to reach for even more illicit power ,","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"called the Trump administration the gravest threat to the rule of law in a generation .","depth":7},{"id":204,"text":"`` I do not take a position on the proper prison term for Mr. Stone ,","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"but it would be a blatant abuse of power","depth":10},{"id":206,"text":"if President Trump has in fact intervened","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"to reverse the recommendations of career prosecutors at the Department of Justice , ''","depth":11},{"id":208,"text":"Schiff said .","depth":8},{"id":209,"text":"`` Doing so would send an unmistakable message","depth":9},{"id":210,"text":"that President Trump will protect those","depth":11},{"id":211,"text":"who lie to Congress","depth":12},{"id":212,"text":"to cover up his own misconduct ,","depth":12},{"id":213,"text":"and that the attorney general will join him in that effort , ''","depth":10},{"id":214,"text":"Schiff said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":215,"text":"Three prosecutors","depth":8},{"id":216,"text":"who worked on the Stone case","depth":8},{"id":217,"text":"quit","depth":7},{"id":218,"text":"soon after the department backtracked on its sentencing memo .","depth":6},{"id":219,"text":"Aaron Zelinsky and Jonathan Kravis also resigned from the DC US Attorney 's office","depth":6},{"id":220,"text":"and Adam Jed and Michael Marando filed memos","depth":7},{"id":221,"text":"to withdraw from the Stone case .","depth":7},{"id":222,"text":"Ironically , the danger","depth":7},{"id":223,"text":"posed to America 's institutions of governance by political interference","depth":7},{"id":224,"text":"was at the center of final arguments in the Stone case","depth":7},{"id":225,"text":"made by Marando .","depth":7},{"id":226,"text":"`` In our institutions of self-governance , committee hearings , courts of law ... truth still matters , ''","depth":6},{"id":227,"text":"Marando said .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":455,"left":404,"right":454,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":404,"left":343,"right":403,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":343,"left":272,"right":342,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":246,"right":271,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":237,"right":245,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":0,"right":236,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":236,"left":231,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":1,"right":230,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":230,"left":2,"right":229,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":229,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":235,"left":234,"right":9,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":234,"left":5,"right":233,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":6,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":232,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":239,"right":244,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":10,"right":238,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":13,"right":243,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":241,"right":242,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":14,"right":240,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":242,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":267,"right":270,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":267,"left":258,"right":266,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":258,"left":254,"right":257,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":251,"right":253,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":251,"left":247,"right":250,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":247,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":21,"right":249,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":22,"right":248,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":25,"right":252,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":252,"left":26,"right":27,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":28,"right":256,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":29,"right":255,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":30,"right":31,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":262,"right":265,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":32,"right":261,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":33,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":34,"right":259,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":35,"right":36,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":265,"left":37,"right":264,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":264,"left":38,"right":263,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":39,"right":40,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":268,"right":269,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":268,"left":41,"right":42,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":43,"right":44,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":342,"left":45,"right":341,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":341,"left":279,"right":340,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":276,"right":278,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":276,"left":273,"right":275,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":273,"left":46,"right":47,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":48,"right":274,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":49,"right":50,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":278,"left":51,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":52,"right":53,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":340,"left":285,"right":339,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":285,"left":282,"right":284,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":282,"left":54,"right":281,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":280,"right":57,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":55,"right":56,"relation":"context","nuclearity"